sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    Title: Stage 3 — CI/CD Pipeline (Full AWS EKS)

    actor DEV as 👨‍💻 Developer
    participant GH as GitHub Actions
    participant SONAR as SonarCloud<br/>(Code Quality)
    participant TRIVY as Trivy<br/>(Vulnerability Scan)
    participant ECR as Amazon ECR
    participant SM as Secrets Manager
    participant TERRAFORM as Terraform Cloud<br/>(IaC)
    participant EKS as AWS EKS
    participant ARGOCD as ArgoCD<br/>(GitOps)
    participant CFT as CloudFormation<br/>(IaC Drift)
    participant CW as CloudWatch<br/>(Monitoring)

    DEV->>GH: git push main

    rect rgba(0, 50, 100, 0.1)
        Note over GH,TRIVY: Pre-deploy checks
        GH->>GH: Unit tests
        GH->>SONAR: Static code analysis
        GH->>TRIVY: Container image scan
        TRIVY-->>GH: ✅ No critical CVEs
    end

    par Container Build & Push
        GH->>ECR: docker build + push<br/>api:v4.0.0
        GH->>SM: Fetch secrets via OIDC role
        Note over GH,SM: No long-lived AWS keys!<br/>Uses GitHub OIDC Provider
    end

    par Infrastructure as Code
        GH->>TERRAFORM: terraform plan
        TERRAFORM->>TERRAFORM: Validate infra changes
        TERRAFORM-->>GH: ✅ Plan approved
        GH->>TERRAFORM: terraform apply
        TERRAFORM->>EKS: Update EKS add-ons / IRSA
        TERRAFORM-->>DEV: ✅ Infra updated
    end

    par GitOps Sync (ArgoCD)
        ArgoCD->>ECR: Pull new image tag
        ArgoCD->>EKS: kubectl apply (auto-sync)
        ArgoCD->>EKS: kubectl rollout status
        ArgoCD-->>DEV: ✅ GitOps sync complete
    end

    rect rgba(0, 100, 0, 0.1)
        Note over EKS,CW: Post-deploy verification
        EKS->>CW: Emit metrics & logs
        CW->>DEV: Slack alert: ✅ Deployed<br/>Pipeline: 3m 42s
        CW->>CW: GuardDuty scan
        CW->>CW: Security Hub findings
    end

    Note over GH,DEV: Full audit trail:<br/>CloudTrail logs every API call<br/>Pipeline run ID in every pod label<br/>Shift-left security baked in
